    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Not this time. To keep the cargo airship steady, we need to arrange
      the crates according to their center of mass.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Center of mass? What\u2019s that exactly?"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Center of mass is the average position of all parts of the object or
      system, which are weighted according to their collective masses.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Like the balancing spot on a seesaw?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 1
    endTime: 2
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Exactly! Formula: COM = (\u03A3 m\u1D62l\u1D62) / M"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 3
    endTime: 4
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: And with just two objects?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 4
    endTime: 5
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: COM = (m1, x1 + m2, x2) / (m1 + m2)
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 6
    endTime: 7
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: So moving heavier crates closer to the center keeps the ship level.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 7
    endTime: 8
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Correct. Now\u2014momentum. It means that things are on the move, and
      is going to take some amounts of effort to stop."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 9
    endTime: 10
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Mass times velocity\u2014so heavier or faster means harder to stop."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 10
    endTime: 11
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Yes. Its unit is kg\xB7m/s. That\u2019s why a speeding crate hits harder
      than a still one."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: So balance controls center of mass, and velocity decides momentum. Both
      matter in flight.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Thanks for the lesson, Gizmo. I think I understand center of mass and
      momentum now.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Great job! You\u2019re ready to test what you\u2019ve learned."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Awesome\u2014time to take the quiz!"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
